<br>
If anyone could post relevant Allakhazam links or tactics links that would be cool too.  This is in the hope of myself and my friends not making total asshats of ourselves if and when we reach these encounters <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
